snippet.title: NND Videos Combined - BS サテラQ わいわいでQ 春の採点4週目 | WaiWai De Q - Haru no Saiten 4
snippet.description:
Original NND URLs:
http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm7442436
http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm7442482
http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm7442587

NND videos that show the peculiar Satellaview quiz game "Satella-Q" in it's "Wai Wai De Q" form, from earlier in the Satellaview's lifespan.
Re-done because the old ones had terrible audio desync issues.

I created this video with the YouTube Video Editor (http://www.youtube.com/editor)
